\cf3 //	 Convolution of two soundfiles -- change this to enable loading of soundfiles from disk, so that you can find the most effective combinations\cf0 \
\cf3 /*\
\
PV_MagMul.ar  (multiplies magnitudes of two inputs, keeps phase of first)\
Convolution.ar (real-time convolver of two continuously changing inputs)\
Convolution2.ar (real-time convolver of two inputs, one of which changes only at triggers)\
\
Also check out:\
	PV_ConformalMap (transformation of complex plane?)\
	PV_HainsworthFoote (spectral onset detection)\
	PV_JensenAndersen (spectral onset detection)\
*/\cf0 \
\cf3 // CONVOLUTION\cf0 \
\
